latestPosts.caption: My father loves life. My father has a passion for travel. My father has a strong sense of self. My father worries about my mother. My father loves dahi. My father has a wealth of knowledge about history, geography, politics, finance, law and people. My father is curious and will never stop learning. My father doesn’t fall for stupid WhatsApp forwards. My father is adored in every social circle he belongs to. My father is confident. My father makes me laugh. My father loves to quote from the movie “Sholay” a lot. My father has a deep relationship with his god. My father is generous. My father is a planner and a do-er in equal measure. My father is goofy. My father loves music. My father likes animals. My father is a cautious optimist. My father is a natural guide. My father taught me to think, to question and to not be afraid. My father loves talking. My father is flawed. My father writes so well. My father can take better care of his health. My father has unwavering faith in his children. My father is my friend. What a blessing. Happy Papa Day❤️
